WEBVTT

1
00:01:00.197 --> 00:01:02.067
来吧，红
Come on, Red. Giddyup.


2
00:01:02.068 --> 00:01:04.069
快起来，来吧。骑他们吧，牛仔。
Giddyup, come on. Ride 'em, cowboy.


3
00:01:04.070 --> 00:01:06.811
我们去抓那些亡命之徒。
Let's get those outlaws.


4
00:01:06.812 --> 00:01:08.160
快到了。来吧!
We're almost there. Come on!


5
00:01:08.161 --> 00:01:11.076
明白了。我们知道了。快到了。
Got it. We got it. We're almost there.


6
00:01:11.077 --> 00:01:12.731
来吧。
Come on.


7
00:01:25.744 --> 00:01:27.137
嘿,博伊德。
Hey, Boyd.


8
00:01:28.138 --> 00:01:31.096
你在玉米地里待了多久?
How long were you out in the corn?


9
00:01:31.097 --> 00:01:34.187
我希望不是又一整晚。
Not all night again, I hope.


10
00:01:53.946 --> 00:01:56.818
我不想让你再哭了，伊登。
I don't want you to cry anymore, Eden.


11
00:02:11.659 --> 00:02:13.660
别担心，伊登。
Don't worry, Eden.


12
00:02:13.661 --> 00:02:16.098
在玉米地里什么都不会死。
Nothing ever really dies in the corn.


13
00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:28.807
博伊德!该死的。你到底去哪儿了?
Boyd! Damn it. Where the hell you been?


14
00:02:34.029 --> 00:02:38.469
博伊德……博伊德,不!
Boyd... Boyd, no!


15
00:02:47.173 --> 00:02:52.046
各单位注意，瑞尔斯通儿童之家发生人质劫持事件。
All units be advised, there is a hostage situation at the Rylstone Children's Home.


16
00:02:52.047 --> 00:02:57.791
当地治安官和他的农民朋友们使用了一种动物镇静气体试图解决这个问题。
The local sheriff and his farmer buddies have used some kind of animal sedative gas to try and solve it.


17
00:02:57.792 --> 00:03:00.968
从所有报道来看，这听起来像是一场灾难。
By all reports, it sounds like a total disaster.


18
00:03:00.969 --> 00:03:02.666
是的，我现在在这里。
Yeah, I'm here now.


19
00:03:02.667 --> 00:03:06.061
这些白痴简直是在往里面灌氟烷想把这孩子弄死。
These idiots are literally pumping halothane in to try to take this kid down.


20
00:03:55.502 --> 00:03:58.374
好吧，我的连任失败了。
Well, there goes my reelection.


21
00:03:58.375 --> 00:04:01.812
唯一的一线希望就是那个该死的太空学员。
The only silver lining is that goddamn space cadet in there.


22
00:04:01.813 --> 00:04:08.906
那个小矮子在玉米地里游荡了四天才有人意识到她不是毒气的受害者之一。
That little runt was wandering around the corn for four days before anybody realized she wasn't one of the casualties from the goddamn gas.


23
00:04:08.907 --> 00:04:15.087
牧师，看看那孩子有没有说过什么能解释他为什么突然发作，杀了那么多人。
Pastor, try and find out if that boy said anything that would explain why he snapped and killed all those people.


24
00:04:25.532 --> 00:04:26.664
所以…
So...


25
00:04:29.710 --> 00:04:37.588
我猜这就是说，经历了这一切之后，你需要一个住的地方，对吧?
I guess it follows that, uh, you'll need a place to live after all this, huh?


26
00:04:40.242 --> 00:04:42.243
谁知道呢?
Who knows?


27
00:04:42.244 --> 00:04:49.556
如果你是个好女孩，也许我们可以让你来和我住在一起。
If you're a good girl, then maybe we could manage it for you to come and live with me.


28
00:04:51.079 --> 00:04:54.560
我有个马厩，里面有几匹老马。
I have a stable with a couple of old nags in it.


29
00:04:54.561 --> 00:04:57.389
你可以挑一辆骑上去。
You can pick one out and ride it.


30
00:04:57.390 --> 00:04:59.260
听起来怎么样?
How's that sound?


31
00:04:59.261 --> 00:05:01.872
该死的!
God dang it!


32
00:05:01.873 --> 00:05:04.223
这件衣服快把我逼疯了!
This one piece is driving me nuts!


33
00:05:11.361 --> 00:05:12.797
哦。
Oh.


34
00:05:17.584 --> 00:05:20.718
她来了。红方王后。
There she is. The Red Queen.


35
00:05:21.675 --> 00:05:24.373
你喜欢红方王后吗?
You like the Red Queen?


36
00:05:24.374 --> 00:05:27.768
红皇后让世界变成她想要的样子。
The Red Queen makes the world the way she wants it to be.


37
00:05:29.379 --> 00:05:34.295
E-Eden,我……我真的很抱歉发生在家里的那些小朋友身上的事。
E-Eden, I'm... I'm really sorry about what happened to all your little friends in the home.


38
00:05:34.296 --> 00:05:36.428
真的。
I really am.


39
00:05:36.429 --> 00:05:39.997
这是个不幸的意外。
It was an unfortunate accident.


40
00:05:39.998 --> 00:05:47.919
我得问你…那个男孩，他说什么了吗?
I-I have to ask you... That boy, did he say anything?


41
00:05:50.617 --> 00:05:52.358
不。不是真的。
No. Not really.


42
00:05:54.186 --> 00:05:58.930
除了说他很抱歉。
Oh, uh, except just to say he was sorry.


43
00:06:00.279 --> 00:06:03.063
抱歉?
Sorry?


44
00:06:03.064 --> 00:06:06.327
抱歉杀了监狱里的所有成年人?
Sorry for killing every adult in the facility?


45
00:06:06.328 --> 00:06:07.981
不。
No.


46
00:06:07.982 --> 00:06:10.855
我觉得他很抱歉没把你们都杀了。
I think he was sorry for not killing all of you.


47
00:06:36.533 --> 00:06:38.969
嘿!回来!
Hey! Get back!


48
00:06:38.970 --> 00:06:40.231
嘿，你怎么了?!
Hey, what's wrong with you?!


49
00:06:40.232 --> 00:06:41.538
这应该是公开的!
That should be public!


50
00:07:15.746 --> 00:07:17.051
酷。
Cool.


51
00:07:23.144 --> 00:07:25.232
看看这些东西。
Look at this stuff.


52
00:07:25.233 --> 00:07:30.542
我警告过他们多少次了?
How many times did I try and warn them?


53
00:07:30.543 --> 00:07:36.330
他们都没看一眼标签就把这些东西埋在地里。
The stuff that they put into this ground without even barely reading a label.


54
00:07:36.331 --> 00:07:42.336
有没有注意到“玉米”和“迷宫”这两个词…就像玉米和拼图……是一样的吗?
Ever notice how the words "maize" and "maze"... Like a corn maize and a puzzle... are the same?


55
00:07:42.337 --> 00:07:45.165
玉米迷宫。
A maze of maize.


56
00:07:45.166 --> 00:07:46.210
奇怪,是吧?
Weird, huh?


57
00:07:46.211 --> 00:07:48.125
当然。“惊人的”。
Sure. "Amazing."


58
00:07:48.126 --> 00:07:49.910
Har-dee-har。咬我。
Har-dee-har. Bite me.


59
00:07:51.042 --> 00:07:53.173
嘿!
Hey!


60
00:07:53.174 --> 00:07:56.568
毒素在腐烂作物的茎叶上生长。
Toxins grow on the stalks and leaves of rotting crops.


61
00:07:56.569 --> 00:07:58.396
这是一种真菌。
It's a fungus.


62
00:07:58.397 --> 00:08:02.662
它会让你生病甚至死亡。
It can make you sick or even die.


63
00:08:06.100 --> 00:08:07.231
是的。
Yeah.


64
00:08:07.232 --> 00:08:09.668
还有幻觉。
And, uh, hallucinations.


65
00:08:09.669 --> 00:08:12.845
-随你怎么说，波。——什么?这是真的。
- Whatever you say, Bo. - What? It's true.


66
00:08:12.846 --> 00:08:16.588
有人说它是塞勒姆女巫审判的罪魁祸首。
You know, some people say it was responsible for the Salem witch trials.


67
00:08:16.589 --> 00:08:18.112
我也很高兴和你聊天，姐姐。
Fun talking to you too, sis.


68
00:08:20.637 --> 00:08:22.551
啊!
Ahh!


69
00:08:22.552 --> 00:08:27.077
嗯!闻闻那些毒素。天鹅绒般柔软可口。
Mmm! Smell those toxins. Velvety and delicious.


70
00:08:27.078 --> 00:08:28.600
-太好了。-茜茜，别说了。
- So good. - Ceece, stop.


71
00:08:28.601 --> 00:08:30.080
我想再来一份。
Think I'll have a second helping.


72
00:08:30.081 --> 00:08:32.038
别说了。别玩那些东西了，好吗?
Cut it out. Stop playing with that stuff, okay?


73
00:08:32.039 --> 00:08:38.958
现在，听我说。我…这不是我带你来的原因，好吗?
Now, listen to me. I... That's not why I brought you out here, okay?


74
00:08:38.959 --> 00:08:40.395
这是。
This is.


75
00:08:41.396 --> 00:08:47.881
我已经一个月没睡了，因为我…
I literally haven't been able to sleep for a month because I...


76
00:08:51.581 --> 00:08:53.104
在这里。
Here.


77
00:09:01.416 --> 00:09:04.070
我下周离开。
I leave next week.


78
00:09:04.071 --> 00:09:09.032
听着，这是微生物学的本科学位。
Look, it's an undergraduate degree in microbiology.


79
00:09:09.033 --> 00:09:11.861
好吧?这不是永恒。
All right? It's not an eternity.


80
00:09:11.862 --> 00:09:13.646
它是。
It is.


81
00:09:16.127 --> 00:09:18.084
它是!你为什么要回来?
It is! Why would you ever come back?


82
00:09:18.085 --> 00:09:20.217
我知道你讨厌这里。
I know you hate it here.


83
00:09:20.218 --> 00:09:22.089
因为。
Because.


84
00:09:23.177 --> 00:09:27.311
因为你。因为爸爸。
Because of you. Because of Dad.


85
00:09:27.312 --> 00:09:33.839
听着，希希，你知道，总有一天你也会离开这里。
And look, Ceece, you know, you'll leave here one day too.


86
00:09:33.840 --> 00:09:35.973
因为我糟糕的成绩?
With my cruddy grades?


87
00:09:37.061 --> 00:09:39.106
我将永远被困在这里。
I'll be stuck here forever.


88
00:09:40.107 --> 00:09:43.327
在这个恐怖垂死的地方。
In this creepy, dying place.


89
00:09:43.328 --> 00:09:45.635
不。瑞尔斯通不会死的。
No. Rylstone's not dying.


90
00:09:47.288 --> 00:09:49.812
这几年过得很艰难。你知道吗?
It's been a hard couple years. You know?


91
00:09:49.813 --> 00:09:51.335
我们犯了很多错误。
A lot of mistakes have been made.


92
00:09:51.336 --> 00:09:54.207
做了很多糟糕透顶的决定。
A lot of shitty, shitty decisions.


93
00:09:54.208 --> 00:10:03.827
但与…花点时间和心思，然后这一切…这是可以解决的。
But with... with a little time and care, then all this... it can be fixed.


94
00:10:05.872 --> 00:10:06.960
是的。
Yeah.


95
00:10:08.745 --> 00:10:10.834
听起来不错，波。
Sounds awesome, Bo.


96
00:10:14.664 --> 00:10:17.622
Eden!天啊，你吓死我们了。
Eden! God, you scared the shit out of us.


97
00:10:17.623 --> 00:10:19.103
认真对待。
Seriously.


98
00:10:20.060 --> 00:10:21.060
假发是怎么回事?
What's with the wig?


99
00:10:21.061 --> 00:10:26.763
今天我是红方王后。
Today I am the Red Queen.


100
00:10:30.070 --> 00:10:31.984
Crud。
Crud.


101
00:10:31.985 --> 00:10:34.334
说到这个我们走吧
Um, speaking of which let's go.


102
00:10:34.335 --> 00:10:36.989
加油，红魔!快起来，来吧。
Come on, Red! Giddyup, come on.


103
00:10:36.990 --> 00:10:39.906
塞西尔，你不会想错过这个的。
Cecil, you're not gonna want to miss this.


104
00:11:32.742 --> 00:11:35.092
沃利·托马斯·普拉特!
Wally Thomas Pratt!


105
00:11:40.314 --> 00:11:48.757
“因为残忍和不寻常地对待你自己的猎犬，你被判处死刑!”
"For the crime of cruel and unusual treatment of your very own hunting dog, you are hereby sentenced to die!"


106
00:11:48.758 --> 00:11:50.541
你杀了吉伯!
You killed Gibber!


107
00:11:50.542 --> 00:11:53.500
嘿!我知道这只是玩玩，但那不是我的错。
Hey! I know this is for play and all, but that wasn't my fault.


108
00:11:53.501 --> 00:11:55.241
我没有给吉伯下毒药。
I didn't give Gibber that poison.


109
00:11:55.242 --> 00:11:56.852
他从捕鼠器里吃的。
He ate it out of some rat trap.


110
00:11:56.853 --> 00:11:59.245
而你却眼睁睁看着他受苦!
And you just watched him suffer!


111
00:11:59.246 --> 00:12:00.856
他只是一只老猎狗。
He was just an old hound dog.


112
00:12:00.857 --> 00:12:02.597
骗子!比利巴!
Liar! Billy Barnes!


113
00:12:03.642 --> 00:12:05.382
狗的杀手!
Dog killer!


114
00:12:05.383 --> 00:12:06.687
嘿,沃利。
Hey, Wally.


115
00:12:06.688 --> 00:12:08.341
去你的，巴恩斯。
Screw you, Barnes.


116
00:12:08.342 --> 00:12:09.603
滚下去，沃利!
Off the edge, Wally!


117
00:12:09.604 --> 00:12:11.997
♬走独木桥，走独木桥♬
♪ Walk the plank, walk the plank ♪


118
00:12:11.998 --> 00:12:14.304
♪走跳板，Wally Thomas Pratt♪
♪ Walk the plank, Wally Thomas Pratt ♪


119
00:12:14.305 --> 00:12:16.480
♬走独木桥，走独木桥♬
♪ Walk the plank, walk the plank ♪


120
00:12:16.481 --> 00:12:18.830
♪走跳板，Wally Thomas Pratt♪
♪ Walk the plank, Wally Thomas Pratt ♪


121
00:12:18.831 --> 00:12:22.312
噢!呀!该死，比利，别用那东西戳我!
Ow! Jeez! Dang it, Billy, quit jabbing me with that thing!


122
00:12:22.313 --> 00:12:24.488
放弃拖延!结束了!
Quit stalling! Off the end!


123
00:12:24.489 --> 00:12:26.011
结束了!
Off the end!


124
00:12:26.012 --> 00:12:28.405
跳!跳!跳!跳!
Jump! Jump! Jump! Jump!


125
00:12:28.406 --> 00:12:29.493
跳!
Jump!


126
00:12:29.494 --> 00:12:32.670
照他们说的做!跳!
Do what they say! Jump!


127
00:12:32.671 --> 00:12:33.889
来吧!
Come on!


128
00:12:33.890 --> 00:12:36.805
嘿!你到底在干什么?
Hey! What the hell are you doing?


129
00:12:36.806 --> 00:12:38.415
嘿,考尔德。
Hey, Calder.


130
00:12:38.416 --> 00:12:40.852
你在我奶奶的车上做什么?
What in frick's name are you doing on my grandma's car?


131
00:12:40.853 --> 00:12:42.115
凸轮吗?
Cam?


132
00:12:43.464 --> 00:12:45.988
下车。滚远点。
Get off. Get the hell off.


133
00:12:45.989 --> 00:12:47.904
你疯了吗?
Are you effing crazy?


134
00:12:49.296 --> 00:12:50.557
你们这些蠢蛋。
You dumb-ass idiots.


135
00:12:50.558 --> 00:12:52.211
你把四分之一的嵌板弄凹了。
You've dented the quarter panels.


136
00:12:52.212 --> 00:12:55.214
你把窗户打碎了。
You cracked the window.


137
00:12:55.215 --> 00:12:56.347
该死的。
Damn.


138
00:12:57.609 --> 00:12:59.349
你甚至把油箱都弄坏了。
You've even busted the gas tank.


139
00:12:59.350 --> 00:13:01.568
等等，考尔德，这是你的车?
Wait, Calder, this is your car?


140
00:13:01.569 --> 00:13:04.310
是的。我的奶奶的。66岁的。
Yeah. My grandma's. '66 Olds.


141
00:13:04.311 --> 00:13:06.965
那为什么要停在这荒郊野外?
So why is it parked out here in the middle of nowhere?


142
00:13:06.966 --> 00:13:08.837
管好你的事怎么样，derp?
How about mind your business, derp?


143
00:13:08.838 --> 00:13:11.971
我想把我奶奶的车停在我爸的地里，我会的，好吗?
I want to park my grandma's car in my dad's field, I will, okay?


144
00:13:14.669 --> 00:13:16.670
你到底在外面干什么?
What the hell are you doing out here anyway?


145
00:13:16.671 --> 00:13:19.282
我们要处决沃利·普拉特。
We're executing Wally Pratt.


146
00:13:19.283 --> 00:13:22.241
他让吉伯痛苦而漫长地死去。
He let Gibber die a long and painful death.


147
00:13:22.242 --> 00:13:24.723
胡扯?不可能。我爱吉伯。
Gibber? No way. I loved Gibber.


148
00:13:25.680 --> 00:13:27.072
螺丝。
Screw that.


149
00:13:27.073 --> 00:13:29.248
和他的混蛋在一起。
Off the edge with his punk ass.


150
00:13:29.249 --> 00:13:31.381
是啊!现在，别再拖延了!
Yeah! Now, quit stalling!


151
00:13:31.382 --> 00:13:33.252
从边缘掉下来!
Off the edge!


152
00:13:33.253 --> 00:13:35.124
——是的!-从边缘掉下来!
- Yeah! - Off the edge!


153
00:13:35.125 --> 00:13:36.517
跳!
Jump!


154
00:13:37.518 --> 00:13:38.693
该死，比利!
Dang it, Billy!


155
00:13:42.523 --> 00:13:46.049
阿奇，准备在他落地时点燃玉米。
Archie, get ready to light up that corn when he lands in it.


156
00:13:47.093 --> 00:13:50.313
哇!等待。你不能这么做。
Whoa! Wait. You can't do that.


157
00:13:50.314 --> 00:13:53.142
那辆车在漏油，空气中弥漫着谷物粉尘?
With that car leaking gas and the grain dust in the air?


158
00:13:53.143 --> 00:13:55.057
那东西就像火药，知道吗?
That stuff is like gunpowder, okay?


159
00:13:55.058 --> 00:13:59.062
什么都不剩了，包括你。
There won't be anything left, including you.


160
00:14:01.716 --> 00:14:04.327
是的。博林是对的。把他推开。
Yeah. Boleyn's right. Just shove him off.


161
00:14:04.328 --> 00:14:06.329
我们假装把他烧死!
We'll pretend the part where we burn him to death!


162
00:14:06.330 --> 00:14:07.852
是啊!
Yeah!


163
00:14:07.853 --> 00:14:11.334
死亡!死亡!死亡!
Death! Death! Death!


164
00:14:11.335 --> 00:14:13.249
从边缘掉下来!
Off the edge!


165
00:14:13.250 --> 00:14:14.815
-把他推下去!-从边缘掉下来!
- Push him off! - Off the edge!


166
00:14:14.816 --> 00:14:16.992
-我不干了。-从边缘掉下来!
- I'm out. - Off the edge!


167
