I'm getting out of here.


193
00:16:17.461 --> 00:16:19.766
是的。
Yeah.


194
00:16:19.767 --> 00:16:24.337
但你要逃的不只是莱尔斯通的死玉米，对吧?
Except it's not just Rylstone's dying corn you're escaping, is it?


195
00:16:26.861 --> 00:16:28.385
别胡扯了。
Come off it.


196
00:16:32.084 --> 00:16:33.694
这是个意外。
It was an accident.


197
00:16:35.392 --> 00:16:41.876
卡尔，你不是…当我笨手笨脚地把他的拳头插在弟弟和他之间时，我的脸撞到了他的拳头。
Cal, you're not... My face hit his fist when I inserted it stupidly between my little brother and him.


198
00:16:43.139 --> 00:16:44.879
事故。
Accident.


199
00:16:45.967 --> 00:16:47.969
我很抱歉。
I'm so sorry.


200
00:16:49.145 --> 00:16:50.623
不要。
Don't be.


201
00:16:50.624 --> 00:16:53.974
为那些没有出路的人感到遗憾。
Be sorry for the ones who don't have a way out.


202
00:16:53.975 --> 00:16:58.501
听着，说到出去…上个周末上学前。
Look, speaking of getting out... Last weekend before school.


203
00:16:58.502 --> 00:17:01.069
