205
00:17:02.593 --> 00:17:05.986
我得留下来，照看我的投资。
I got to hang back, look after my investments.


206
00:17:05.987 --> 00:17:10.252
看来你和我最后一次可以独享瑞尔斯通了。
Guess you and I will be having Rylstone all to ourselves one last time.


207
00:17:10.253 --> 00:17:13.385
只有我们和小家伙们。
Just us and the little ones.


208
00:17:13.386 --> 00:17:15.214
不要忘记那些小事。
Don't forget the little ones.


209
00:17:18.435 --> 00:17:19.740
再见。
See you.


210
00:17:20.785 --> 00:17:22.091
再见。
See you.


211
00:19:02.800 --> 00:19:04.976
-走跳板!——上帝!
- Walk the plank! - God!


212
00:19:05.933 --> 00:19:10.023
耶稣,什么…塞勒姆女巫审判已经结束了吗?
Jesus, what... So are the Salem witch trials over already?


213
00:19:10.024 --> 00:19:12.722
非常甜蜜。沃利吓坏了。
It was pretty sweet. Wally was freaking out.


214
00:19:12.723 --> 00:19:17.553
每个人都在尖叫，大喊大叫，在玉米地里跳舞。
