215
00:19:17.554 --> 00:19:19.250
真是太棒了。
It was pretty dope.


216
00:19:19.251 --> 00:19:21.166
妈妈?
Mom?


217
00:19:23.037 --> 00:19:24.996
Ceece。我们走吧。来吧。
Ceece. Let's go. Come on.


218
00:19:30.349 --> 00:19:33.786
希希，这是爸爸妈妈之间的事。
Ceece, that's between Mom and Dad.


219
00:19:33.787 --> 00:19:36.789
好吧?Ceece。来吧。
Okay? Ceece. Come on.


220
00:19:36.790 --> 00:19:39.401
波，你太瞎了。
Bo, you are so blind.


221
00:19:39.402 --> 00:19:40.750
这和妈妈无关。
It's not about Mom.


222
00:19:40.751 --> 00:19:43.232
这和爸爸无关。
It's not about Dad.


223
00:19:44.972 --> 00:19:46.930
是关于瑞尔斯通的。
It's about Rylstone.


224
00:19:46.931 --> 00:19:54.154
而是关于这个地方已经支离破碎了甚至没有人愿意去修复它。
It's about this place that's so broken that nobody even gives a damn enough to try to fix it.


225
00:19:54.155 --> 00:19:57.681
不过，我想这就不是你的问题了，对吧，菠?
But, then, I guess that's not your problem anymore, is it, Bo?


226
00:19:59.248 --> 00:20:00.945
享受波士顿。
Enjoy Boston.


227
00:20:20.181 --> 00:20:23.445
玉米……我们的玉米…正在消亡。
Corn... our corn... is dying.


228
00:20:23.446 --> 00:20:25.011
-是的。-是的。
- Yeah. - Yeah.


229
00:20:25.012 --> 00:20:32.149
在离这里不到500码的田野里，放眼望去，是一片垂死的棕色海洋。
In the fields not 500 yards from here, as far as the eye can see, is a sea of dying brown.


230
00:20:32.150 --> 00:20:38.416
那些伴随我们长大的，祖先种在这里的金色谷物去哪了?
What happened to the glorious golden grain that we grew up with, that our forefathers planted here?


231
00:20:38.417 --> 00:20:40.026
我们知道发生了什么。
Well, we know what happened.


232
00:20:40.027 --> 00:20:44.770
我们投票了，大多数人……你知道，我不同意……统治。
We voted, and a majority... A majority you know I disagreed with... ruled.


233
00:20:44.771 --> 00:20:52.474
所以我们邀请了大玉米公司GrowSynth，带着他们的除草剂和转基因作物进入我们的田地。
So we invited Big Corn, GrowSynth, right into our fields with their arsenal of herbicides and GMOs.


234
00:20:52.475 --> 00:20:54.476
看看玉米发生了什么。
And look what happened to the corn.


235
00:20:54.477 --> 00:20:55.695
我都不知道。
Just didn't even know.


236
00:20:57.218 --> 00:20:58.654
我的玉米就是这样。
That's what happened to my corn.


237
00:20:58.655 --> 00:21:01.266
-没错。-事情就是这样。
- That's right. - That's what happened.


238
00:21:05.792 --> 00:21:09.186
指责是没有意义的，因为木已成舟。
There's no sense pointing fingers because what's done is done.


239
00:21:09.187 --> 00:21:12.537
但这意味着我们必须面对一个新的现实。
But what that means is we have to face a new reality.


240
00:21:12.538 --> 00:21:20.372
也许，只是也许，所有的手指都指向了错误的方向。
Or maybe, just maybe, all those fingers are pointing the wrong way anyhow.


241
00:21:22.592 --> 00:21:32.592
我们的玉米遭受的枯萎病，也许与GrowSynth或我们放入土壤中的任何转基因生物关系不大，更多的是与我们自己有关，与你们有关。
That blight that struck our corn, maybe it's got a lot less to do with GrowSynth or any GMOs we put in our soil and more to do with us, more to do with you.


242
00:21:38.521 --> 00:21:40.522
坐吧，老头。
Sit down, old man.


243
00:21:40.523 --> 00:21:50.523
也许在我们的玉米地里发生的事情与其说是一场农业灾难不如说是一种道德和精神上的憎恶吞没了这个小镇!
Maybe what's happening out there in our corn is less about an agricultural calamity and more about a moral and spiritual abomination that has engulfed this town!


244
00:21:55.276 --> 00:22:01.978
好吧，既然我们听够了那些道貌不扬的，神圣的滚马废话。
Okay, now that we're done listening to that sanctimonious, Holy Rolling horse crap.


245
00:22:01.979 --> 00:22:05.460
这与你的欺骗和背后的中伤无关。
It isn't about any of the cheating or the backstabbing that's been going on.


246
00:22:05.461 --> 00:22:08.027
它只关乎一件事。
It's about one thing and one thing only.


247
00:22:08.028 --> 00:22:10.073
现在，我们被卖了一大堆豆子。
Now, we was sold a hill of beans.


248
00:22:10.074 --> 00:22:11.161
-没错。——是的!
- That's right. - Yeah!


249
00:22:11.162 --> 00:22:18.342
他们说，我们所要做的就是把这个，把那个放进土壤里，改变我们的玉米，这样我们就可以卖更多的苏打水给第三世界的穷孩子。
All we had to do, they said, was put this put that in the soil and alter our corn so we could sell more soda to the poor kids in the Third World.


250
00:22:18.343 --> 00:22:20.388
他们说，这样做，我们就发财了。
Do that, they said, and we'd be rich.


251
00:22:20.389 --> 00:22:22.390
比我们想象的还要富有。
Richer than we could dream.


252
00:22:22.391 --> 00:22:24.479
但相反，看看发生了什么。
But instead, look at what happened.


253
00:22:24.480 --> 00:22:26.785
玉米病和经济灾难。
Sick corn and economic disaster.


254
00:22:26.786 --> 00:22:30.049
这就是瑞尔斯通必须留下玉米的原因。
And that's why Rylstone has to leave corn behind.


255
00:22:30.050 --> 00:22:31.834
这就是我们能做的。
This is how we can do it.


256
00:22:31.835 --> 00:22:33.226
补贴。
Subsidies.


257
00:22:33.227 --> 00:22:34.750
补贴吗?
Subsidies?


258
00:22:34.751 --> 00:22:39.319
联邦政府将补贴……付给我们……不是种玉米。
Federal government will subsidize... pay us... Not to grow corn.


259
00:22:39.320 --> 00:22:45.064
但这个项目的财政年度还有不到两天就结束了，所以我们必须答应，而且必须现在就做。
