260
00:22:45.065 --> 00:22:52.376
我们的推土机就在镇边上准备挖沟埋我们的玉米。
We got earthmovers right at the edge of town ready to dig the trench to bury our corn.


261
00:22:52.377 --> 00:22:54.726
我和你一样不想这样。
And I don't want this any more than you do.


262
00:22:54.727 --> 00:23:02.430
听着，这并不理想，我承认，但我觉得我们别无选择。
And look, it's not ideal, I admit that, but I don't think we have a choice.


263
00:23:02.431 --> 00:23:05.129
好吧，我不同意，爸爸。
Yeah, well, I disagree, Dad.


264
00:23:08.654 --> 00:23:10.960
你们都应该感到羞愧。
You all should be ashamed.


265
00:23:10.961 --> 00:23:17.923
