268
00:23:27.238 --> 00:23:35.550
内斗，再一次以最快的速度出卖我们的灵魂，只是卖给了另一个主人。
Infighting and selling all our souls all over again as fast as you can, just to a different master.


269
00:23:35.551 --> 00:23:38.944
