278
00:24:12.588 --> 00:24:14.197
那我们来投票吧。
So let's put it to a vote.


279
00:24:14.198 --> 00:24:19.419
不，罗伯特，我真的必须……请坐，牧师。没人在乎。
No, Robert, I-I really must... Sit down, Pastor. No one cares.


280
00:24:19.420 --> 00:24:22.684
