Yeah. Florida time-share, here I come.


283
00:24:27.820 --> 00:24:29.865
玉米经济见鬼去吧。
Corn economy can kiss my ass.


284
00:24:29.866 --> 00:24:30.996
——是的!——是的!
- Yeah! - Yeah!


285
00:24:30.997 --> 00:24:32.738
看到举手了吗?
See a show of hands?


286
00:24:36.568 --> 00:24:39.919
