288
00:24:47.013 --> 00:24:49.101
不是我们。
Not us.


289
00:24:49.102 --> 00:24:51.495
孩子们。
The children.


290
00:24:51.496 --> 00:24:53.323
他们是对的。
They're right.


291
00:24:53.324 --> 00:24:55.673
这也是孩子们的未来。
It's the little ones' futures too.


292
00:24:55.674 --> 00:24:58.371
是啊，他们连投票权都没有。
Yeah, they don't even get a vote, a say.


293
00:24:58.372 --> 00:25:01.026
因为波是对的。我们有一个选择。
'Cause Bo is right. We have a choice.


294
00:25:01.027 --> 00:25:02.855
好了，废话够多了。
All right, enough horseshit.


295
00:25:04.378 --> 00:25:06.772
孩子吗?有发言权?
Children? Having a say?


296
00:25:08.165 --> 00:25:11.602
我以为17岁的孩子顶嘴已经够糟了。
I thought 17-year-olds mouthing off was bad enough.


297
00:25:11.603 --> 00:25:14.605
愚蠢的孩子。
Stupid kids.


298
00:25:14.606 --> 00:25:15.999
听的,听。
Hear, hear.


299
00:25:18.479 --> 00:25:19.611
小孩子!
Little kids!


300
00:25:21.004 --> 00:25:22.309
投票!
Voting!


301
00:25:25.443 --> 00:25:27.923
好吧，我建议你回家玩你的玩具。
Yeah, well, I vote you go home and play with your toys.


302
00:25:27.924 --> 00:25:29.577
好吗，小姑娘?
Okay, little girl?


303
00:25:29.578 --> 00:25:33.363
听起来怎么样?是吗?
How does that sound? Yeah?


304
00:25:33.364 --> 00:25:36.148
你也是，孩子。你就等我回家吧。
You too, boy. You just wait till I get home.


305
00:25:36.149 --> 00:25:37.890
你等着吧，孩子。
You just wait, boy.


306
00:25:39.109 --> 00:25:41.502
嘿，来吧!嘿!嘿!
Hey, come on! Hey! Hey!


307
00:25:45.115 --> 00:25:46.899
看在上帝的份上，那是个孩子。
That's a child, for Christ's sake.


308
00:25:55.038 --> 00:25:56.604
——嘿!-你会没事的。
- Hey! - You're gonna be fine.


309
00:25:56.605 --> 00:25:59.651
好了，别闹了。这就够了。别闹了!
All right, knock it off. That's enough. Knock it off!


310
00:26:01.348 --> 00:26:03.262
你怎么了?
What is wrong with you?


311
00:26:03.263 --> 00:26:05.395
