Okay. It's settled.


312
00:26:05.396 --> 00:26:10.792
不到48小时，瑞尔斯通的玉米就会永远消失。
In less than 48 hours, corn will be dead in Rylstone forever.


313
00:26:10.793 --> 00:26:13.403
是的。谢谢你！
Yes. Thank you.


314
00:26:13.404 --> 00:26:15.536
