看在上帝的份上，你以为你在干什么?
What in God's name do you think you're doing?


496
00:48:28.868 --> 00:48:31.044
做出裁决。
Rendering the verdict.


497
00:48:31.045 --> 00:48:33.568
你就等着我抓到你吧。
You just wait till I get my hands on you.


498
00:48:33.569 --> 00:48:34.743
你这个小贱人。
You little, bitch.


499
00:48:34.744 --> 00:48:36.963
哦!真的吗?
Oh! Really?


500
00:48:36.964 --> 00:48:38.616
你想惹我吗?
You want to mess with me?


501
00:48:38.617 --> 00:48:41.228
是的。好的,很好。是的。让我们玩。
Yeah. Okay, fine. Yeah. Let's play.


502
00:48:41.229 --> 00:48:43.882
史蒂夫!乔!我们走吧!
Steve! Joe! Let's go!


503
00:48:43.883 --> 00:48:45.493
Eden。
Eden.


504
00:48:45.494 --> 00:48:47.539
-伊登，不要，求你了。-你没必要这么做。
- Eden, no, please. - You don't have to do this.


505
00:48:59.551 --> 00:49:01.553
不!你不能这么做!
No! You can't do this!


506
00:49:04.034 --> 00:49:05.513
Eden。Eden!
Eden. Eden!


507
00:49:05.514 --> 00:49:07.037
让我们出去!
Let us out!


508
00:49:12.782 --> 00:49:13.870
停!
Stop!


509
00:49:19.963 --> 00:49:21.007
博,不!
Bo, no!


510
00:49:21.008 --> 00:49:24.185
妈妈!
Mom!


511
00:49:30.800 --> 00:49:32.062
不!
No!


512
00:49:36.675 --> 00:49:38.155
你在干什么?!
What are you doing?!


513
00:49:39.722 --> 00:49:41.592
不,不!
No, no!


514
00:49:41.593 --> 00:49:42.681
停!
Stop!


515
00:49:48.818 --> 00:49:50.819
不，别这么做!
No, don't do it!


516
00:49:50.820 --> 00:49:53.126
停!不!
Stop! No!


517
00:49:53.127 --> 00:49:54.258
不!
No!


518
00:50:05.226 --> 00:50:08.055
妈妈!妈妈!
Mom! Mom!


519
00:50:54.927 --> 00:50:56.103
塞西尔。
Cecil.


520
00:51:17.863 --> 00:51:19.387
饲料。
Feed.


521
00:51:31.312 --> 00:51:33.096
妈妈。
Mom.


522
00:51:36.404 --> 00:51:38.145
我很抱歉。
I am sorry.


523
00:52:14.442 --> 00:52:16.357
我爸爸是对的。
My dad was right.


524
00:52:18.620 --> 00:52:22.537
他警告我，如果我想弥补，只会让事情更糟。
He warned me if I tried to fix this I'd only make it worse.


525
00:52:24.365 --> 00:52:26.584
所以，如果可以的话，就出去吧。
So get out if you can.


526
00:52:27.933 --> 00:52:29.457
拯救自己。
Save yourselves.


527
00:52:33.983 --> 00:52:37.725
但是我爸爸还活着。
But my dad is still alive.


528
00:52:37.726 --> 00:52:44.601
所以我要留下来阻止伊登把他也杀了。
So I'm gonna stay and stop Eden from killing him too.


529
00:52:44.602 --> 00:52:46.299
是的。
Yeah.


530
00:52:46.300 --> 00:52:48.039
好的。
Okay.


531
00:52:48.040 --> 00:52:50.564
好的,Bo。
Okay, Bo.


532
00:52:50.565 --> 00:52:53.523
去烛台吧。
Well, go to Candlestick.


533
00:52:53.524 --> 00:52:55.526
寻求帮助。
And get help.


534
00:53:54.150 --> 00:53:55.369
你好,Bo。
Hi, Bo.


535
00:53:57.371 --> 00:54:00.155
伊登，你不能。
Eden, you can't.


536
00:54:00.156 --> 00:54:02.550
你不能这样做。
You cannot do this.


537
00:54:05.466 --> 00:54:10.166
他们杀了他们碰过的所有东西。
They kill everything they touch.


538
00:54:11.689 --> 00:54:15.475
让他们接受审判是你的主意。
Putting them on trial was your idea.


539
00:54:15.476 --> 00:54:17.391
你以为会发生什么?
What did you think would happen?


540
00:54:19.697 --> 00:54:22.221
不是这个。
Not this.


541
00:54:23.745 --> 00:54:26.181
是我们对他们。
It's us against them.


542
00:54:26.182 --> 00:54:28.053
你站在哪一边?
Whose side are you on?


543
00:54:36.540 --> 00:54:39.760
你要拿我父亲和其他人怎么办?
What are you gonna do with my father and the others?


544
00:54:39.761 --> 00:54:42.677
我要把他们送到玉米地里去，菠。
I'm gonna send them out to the corn, Bo.


545
00:54:45.723 --> 00:54:50.119
他生病了。他需要进食。
He's sick. He needs to feed.


546
00:54:50.685 --> 00:54:52.120
他吗?
He?


547
00:54:52.121 --> 00:54:54.819
行走的人。
He Who Walks.


548
00:54:57.996 --> 00:54:59.694
我在那里的那个星期……
That week I was out there...


549
00:55:02.044 --> 00:55:07.744
独自在玉米地里游荡……他跟我说话了。
wandering alone in the corn... he talked to me.


550
00:55:07.745 --> 00:55:11.793
他照顾我。
He took care of me.


551
00:55:15.797 --> 00:55:19.191
瑞尔斯通没有一个成年人为我这样做过。
No adult in Rylstone ever did that for me.


552
00:55:21.019 --> 00:55:24.109
所以现在我要照顾他。
So now I'm going to take care of him.


553
00:55:27.461 --> 00:55:30.768
杀死所有的成年人?
By killing all the adults?


554
00:55:32.466 --> 00:55:34.728
首先。
For starters.


555
00:55:34.729 --> 00:55:38.384
波，他们吃了玉米种子。
They ate the seed-corn, Bo.


556
00:55:38.385 --> 00:55:40.387
现在是时候付出代价了。
Now it's time to pay the price.


557
00:55:42.693 --> 00:55:46.392
如果我们中有人能离开这里，去烛台，我们就能得到帮助，好吗?
If one of us can just get out of here, make it to Candlestick, we can get help, all right?


558
00:55:46.393 --> 00:55:48.873
看看这个!
Check this out!


559
00:55:50.048 --> 00:55:51.788
这太疯狂了。爸爸，我需要你相信我。
This is insanity. Dad, I need you to trust me.


560
00:55:51.789 --> 00:55:55.749
现在，他们想知道我站在哪一边，所以我需要你完全按我说的做。
Right now, they want to know who's side I'm on, so I need you to do exactly what I say.


561
00:55:55.750 --> 00:55:59.317
听着，他们想带你们去玉米地里。
Listen, they want to take you all out into the corn.


562
00:55:59.318 --> 00:56:00.797
——什么?对什么?——走吧!走吧!
- What? What for? - Go! Go!


563
00:56:00.798 --> 00:56:02.757
你会很安全的。你可以寻求帮助。
You'll be safe. You can get help.


564
00:56:10.895 --> 00:56:20.034
如果那个生物想让我们去玉米地里，那我们就应该做完全相反的事!
If that creature wants us to go into the corn, then we should be doing the exact opposite!


565
00:56:20.035 --> 00:56:21.775
我不会担心的。
I wouldn't worry about it.


566
00:56:21.776 --> 00:56:25.648
反正你也不会去玉米地里。
You were never going into the corn anyway.


567
00:56:25.649 --> 00:56:27.476
因为你挺身而出
Because you stood up for it.


568
00:56:27.477 --> 00:56:29.870
是的。没错，伊登。
Yes. That's right, Eden.


569
00:56:29.871 --> 00:56:32.481
玉米的死跟我一点关系都没有。
I never had a thing to do with killing the corn.


570
00:56:32.482 --> 00:56:36.180
事实上，我强烈反对!
In fact, I-I spoke out strongly against it!


571
00:56:36.181 --> 00:56:39.749
伊登，还记得在寄养家庭发生的事吗?
Eden, remember that thing that happened in the foster home?


572
00:56:39.750 --> 00:56:43.667
哦。谁收留了你?
Ohh. Who took you in, hmm?


573
00:56:46.975 --> 00:56:49.846
是你，牧师。你所做的。
It was you, Pastor. You did.


574
00:56:49.847 --> 00:56:52.632
你收留了我。
You took me in.


575
00:56:52.633 --> 00:56:55.984
你从未像其他人那样对谷物犯过罪。
You never sinned against the corn like all the rest.


576
00:57:05.472 --> 00:57:07.777
但是，拜托，牧师。
But, come on, Pastor.


577
00:57:07.778 --> 00:57:09.649
你犯了罪。
You did sin.


578
00:57:09.650 --> 00:57:11.042
不是吗?
Didn't you?


579
00:57:17.048 --> 00:57:20.224
——够了!-闭嘴。
- Enough! - Shut up.


580
00:57:20.225 --> 00:57:22.358
不!
No!


581
00:57:25.187 --> 00:57:28.189
不,Eden!不，求你了，不要!
No, Eden! No, please, no!


582
00:57:28.190 --> 00:57:29.582
不，伊登，不!
No, Eden, no!


583
00:57:29.583 --> 00:57:33.977
不，不，不，不!
No, no, no, no!


584
00:57:33.978 --> 00:57:36.372
不，伊登，不!
No, Eden, no!


585
00:57:37.504 --> 00:57:39.548
上帝!哦，天哪，不!
God! Oh, God, no!


586
00:57:39.549 --> 00:57:40.680
拜托!
Please!


587
00:57:40.681 --> 00:57:43.074
不,Eden!
No, Eden!


588
00:57:47.252 --> 00:57:49.254
不,不!
No, no!


589
00:57:50.386 --> 00:57:54.608
天啊，不，不!
God, no, no!


590
00:58:02.746 --> 00:58:04.487
哦,Eden…
Oh, Eden...


591
00:58:29.947 --> 00:58:31.557
波，她在哪?
Bo, where is she?


592
00:58:31.558 --> 00:58:33.123
求你了，别问我这个。别问我妈妈的事。
Please, don't ask me that. Don't ask me about Mom.


593
00:58:33.124 --> 00:58:34.385
我要知道我妻子在哪里!
I need to know where my wife is!


594
00:58:34.386 --> 00:58:35.648
停!
Stop!


595
00:58:35.649 --> 00:58:37.519
听着，你得去玉米地里。
Listen, you need to go out to the corn.


596
00:58:37.520 --> 00:58:39.652
就是这样。这是我们寻求帮助的机会。
That's it. This is our chance to get help.


597
00:58:39.653 --> 00:58:41.611
好吧?就是它了。
Okay? This is it.


598
00:58:44.440 --> 00:58:46.050
好的。我去。
Okay. I'll go.


599
00:58:47.138 --> 00:58:49.879
但你会战斗。好吧?
But you fight. All right?


600
00:58:49.880 --> 00:58:50.967
是的。
Yes.


601
00:58:50.968 --> 00:58:52.448
我爱你。
I love you.


602
00:58:54.798 --> 00:58:56.147
我也爱你。
I love you too.


603
00:59:04.242 --> 00:59:06.504
你做得很好。
You did good.


604
00:59:06.505 --> 00:59:08.072
他今晚会吃得很饱的。
He'll feed well tonight.


605
00:59:09.421 --> 00:59:10.509
放下枪，小卡。
Drop it, Cam.


606
00:59:12.337 --> 00:59:14.470
她不是威胁。
She's not a threat.


607
00:59:23.566 --> 00:59:25.654
好的,爸爸。
Okay, Dad.


608
00:59:25.655 --> 00:59:27.656
我会的。
I will.


609
00:59:27.657 --> 00:59:29.441
我会战斗。
I will fight.


610
00:59:53.727 --> 00:59:55.684
猜猜还有什么。
And guess what else.


611
00:59:55.685 --> 00:59:59.775
从现在起，里尔斯通不许任何人出入!
From now on, no one in Rylstone and no one out!


612
00:59:59.776 --> 01:00:03.257
如果有人想在这里停下来，猜猜我们要做什么。
And if anyone cares to stop here, guess what we're gonna do.


613
01:00:03.258 --> 01:00:05.694
带他们!把他们带到玉米地里去!
Take them! Take them into the corn!


614
01:00:05.695 --> 01:00:08.218
这是正确的。把它们放到玉米地里。
That's right. Get them into the corn.


615
01:00:08.219 --> 01:00:11.657
因为我们不需要他们提供的任何东西!
Because we don't need a single thing they have to offer!


616
01:00:11.658 --> 01:00:17.314
我们需要的一切都在这里，就在那片田野里。
Everything we've ever needed is right here, right out there in those fields.


617
01:00:17.315 --> 01:00:21.710
玉米，土地，会照顾它的孩子。
The corn, the earth, will take care of its children.


618
01:00:21.711 --> 01:00:27.237
现在这是我们的世界，我们要改变一下，按我们想要的方式经营。
This is our world now, and we're gonna run it the way we want for a change.


619
01:00:27.238 --> 01:00:28.630
我们要好好经营!
And we're gonna run it right!


620
01:00:28.631 --> 01:00:29.936
没错!
Right!


621
01:00:29.937 --> 01:00:32.590
也不只是瑞尔斯通一个人。
And isn't just gonna be Rylstone either.


622
01:00:32.591 --> 01:00:35.158
我们要把消息传遍全国。
We're gonna spread the word all across this country.


623
01:00:35.159 --> 01:00:37.465
你以为没有像我们这样的人吗?
You think there aren't others like us?


624
01:00:37.466 --> 01:00:41.730
孩子们眼睁睁地看着自己的世界和未来被出卖?
Kids seeing their world and future just being traded away?


625
01:00:41.731 --> 01:00:45.734
他们也会夺回自己的城镇，让整个世界恢复正常!
Well, they're gonna take their towns, too, and make this whole world right again!


626
01:00:45.735 --> 01:00:52.002
——对吧!——对吧!
- Right! - Right!


627
01:00:56.528 --> 01:00:57.791
比如这个。
Like this thing.


628
01:01:03.884 --> 01:01:08.409
它要利用我们，要出卖我们的未来。
It was going to use us, was going to sell our future.


629
01:01:08.410 --> 01:01:11.238
所以我们应该把她的头砍下来，对吧，菠?
So we should cut her head off, right, Bo?


630
01:01:11.239 --> 01:01:12.457
不!
No!


631
01:01:16.157 --> 01:01:17.766
我的意思是，是的。
I mean, yes.


632
01:01:17.767 --> 01:01:18.899
是的。
Yes.


633
01:01:20.552 --> 01:01:21.770
她犯了罪。
She sinned.


634
01:01:21.771 --> 01:01:25.078
她得罪了你。
She sinned against you.


635
01:01:25.079 --> 01:01:27.124
对我们所有人。
Against all of us.


636
01:01:29.692 --> 01:01:34.218
所以我们不应该在这里浪费她的血。
And that's why we shouldn't waste her blood here.


637
01:01:35.350 --> 01:01:40.268
我可以把她送到玉米地里去。
Not when I can send her into the corn.


638
01:01:41.312 --> 01:01:43.401
这是个好主意，菠。
That's a pretty good idea, Bo.


639
01:02:24.442 --> 01:02:26.140
但是,博…
But, Bo...


640
01:02:30.884 --> 01:02:35.802
更好的办法是直接带她去见他。
An even better idea would be to take her straight to him.


641
01:02:43.418 --> 01:02:45.115
这里。
This way.


642
01:05:16.875 --> 01:05:18.225
就是这样。
That's it.


643
01:05:21.141 --> 01:05:22.185
带她上去。
Take her up.


644
01:05:42.989 --> 01:05:44.642
门。
Doors.


645
01:05:55.697 --> 01:05:57.351
行走的人!
He Who Walks!


646
01:05:59.266 --> 01:06:00.397
来了!
Come!


647
01:06:01.659 --> 01:06:03.531
到我们这儿来!
Come to us!


648
01:06:35.911 --> 01:06:38.217
Eden。
Eden.


649
01:06:38.218 --> 01:06:44.005
那个行走的人，他不存在。
He Who Walks, he doesn't exist.


650
01:06:44.006 --> 01:06:46.574
你竟敢这么说!
Don't you dare say that!


651
01:07:05.897 --> 01:07:07.029
待回来。
Stay back.


652
01:08:07.916 --> 01:08:10.048
这不可能是真的。
It can't be real.


653
01:08:39.556 --> 01:08:40.818
啊!
Aah!


654
01:08:51.220 --> 01:08:54.963
帮帮我!
Help me!


655
01:08:59.663 --> 01:09:01.665
你伤不了我的，菠。
You can't hurt me, Bo.


656
01:09:31.260 --> 01:09:33.870
天啊，你们这些白痴!你们这些该死的小白痴!
God, you idiots! You're goddamn little idiots!


657
01:09:33.871 --> 01:09:35.395
振作起来。
Brace yourself.


658
01:09:36.047 --> 01:09:39.181
你是…你疯了吗?!
Are you... Are you crazy?!


659
01:09:41.270 --> 01:09:43.532
粮食粉尘。
Grain dust.


660
01:09:43.533 --> 01:09:44.838
还记得吗?
Remember?


661
01:09:44.839 --> 01:09:47.319
这地方到处都是。
This place is full of it.


662
01:09:47.320 --> 01:09:51.671
你一点火，这地方就会被炸飞。
You light a fire, this whole place will blow sky high.


663
01:09:51.672 --> 01:09:58.679
玉米和里面的东西都会烧起来。
The corn and everything in it will burn.


664
01:10:08.819 --> 01:10:09.951
很好。
Fine.


665
01:10:12.823 --> 01:10:14.390
我们把她剁了吧。
Let's chop her up.


666
01:10:18.742 --> 01:10:20.657
继续。得到她。
Go on. Get her.


667
01:10:41.025 --> 01:10:43.070
来吧!
Come on!


668
01:10:43.071 --> 01:10:44.593
我们走吧!
Let's go!


669
01:10:44.594 --> 01:10:46.466
到玉米地里去!
Into the corn!


670
01:10:53.211 --> 01:10:54.343
来吧!
Come on!


671
01:11:02.960 --> 01:11:05.049
来吧!
Come on!


672
01:11:52.053 --> 01:11:53.532
爸爸。
Dad.


673
01:11:53.533 --> 01:11:55.448
我很抱歉。
I'm so sorry.


674
01:12:23.171 --> 01:12:25.391
帮助我。
Help me.


675
01:15:15.735 --> 01:15:18.215
车!是的!
Car! Yes!


676
01:15:24.308 --> 01:15:25.919
钥匙，钥匙，钥匙。
Keys, keys, keys.


677
01:17:01.057 --> 01:17:02.972
去他妈的。
Fuck that shit.


678
01:17:15.289 --> 01:17:16.464
不。不。
No. No.


679
01:17:25.516 --> 01:17:27.388
不，不，不。
No, no, no, no.


680
01:17:37.877 --> 01:17:40.053
哦，谢谢。哦，谢天谢地。
Oh, thank you. Oh, thank God.


681
01:17:42.925 --> 01:17:44.492
你好,Bo。
Hi, Bo.


682
01:17:47.364 --> 01:17:48.714
Eden。
Eden.


683
01:17:50.803 --> 01:17:52.979
Eden,Eden。
Eden, Eden.


684
01:17:54.284 --> 01:17:55.546
耶稣。
Jesus.


685
01:17:58.071 --> 01:18:04.511
这……这太疯狂了。
T-This... This is madness.


686
01:18:04.512 --> 01:18:07.341
疯狂,疯狂。
Craziness, insanity.


687
01:18:10.736 --> 01:18:11.998
你知道吗?
You know?


688
01:18:14.043 --> 01:18:17.002
是的。这太疯狂了。
Yeah. It's pretty crazy.


689
01:18:17.003 --> 01:18:18.395
我会告诉你的。
I'll give you that.


690
01:18:33.759 --> 01:18:35.499
那是什么，伊登?
What is that, Eden?


691
01:18:40.853 --> 01:18:42.115
哦。
Oh.


692
01:18:43.420 --> 01:18:44.639
这一点。
This.


693
01:18:46.641 --> 01:18:48.251
肯定的，菠。
Depositive bolt, Bo.


694
01:18:49.078 --> 01:18:51.298
你知道，牛枪。
You know, a cattle gun.


695
01:18:53.387 --> 01:18:55.128
我知道你在想什么。
I know what you're thinking.


696
01:18:57.130 --> 01:18:59.392
算了吧。
Forget it.


697
01:18:59.393 --> 01:19:01.830
你知道这里不止我一个人。
You know I'm not the only one out here.


698
01:19:21.981 --> 01:19:23.983
已经过了我的就寝时间。
It's past my bedtime.


699
01:19:25.680 --> 01:19:26.812
我们走吧。
Let's go.


700
01:19:29.075 --> 01:19:31.120
至少最后一根烟?
A l-last cigarette at least?


701
01:19:33.035 --> 01:19:34.297
你抽烟吗?
You smoke?


702
01:19:38.345 --> 01:19:44.568
坏习惯。我…正要辞职。
Bad habit. I... was about to quit.


703
01:20:38.187 --> 01:20:39.710
来吧。
Come on.


704
01:20:53.159 --> 01:20:54.900
跪下来。
Get down on your knees.


705
01:21:16.834 --> 01:21:18.749
别害怕，菠。
Don't be scared, Bo.


706
01:21:20.838 --> 01:21:22.623
嘿,Eden?
Hey, Eden?


707
01:21:24.930 --> 01:21:34.930
你真的以为你把我浸在拖拉机燃料里的那一刻，我就不会确定我的结果是正确的…
You really think the second you soaked me in all that tractor fuel, that I wasn't gonna make sure I ended up right...


708
01:21:42.425 --> 01:21:43.731
在这里吗?
here?


709
01:21:51.347 --> 01:21:52.914
燃烧。
Burn.


710
01:22:31.170 --> 01:22:32.432
不。
No.


711
01:22:51.190 --> 01:22:53.496
不，不，不!
No, no, no!


712
01:23:19.261 --> 01:23:25.050
烛台和方圆几英里内的其他人很快就会到这里。
Candlestick and everyone else for miles around will be here soon.


713
01:23:26.225 --> 01:23:29.401
面对它。
Face it.


714
01:23:29.402 --> 01:23:31.665
结束了。
It's done.


715
01:23:51.467 --> 01:23:54.253
你的幻想结束了，伊登。
Your fantasy's finished, Eden.


716
01:24:37.339 --> 01:24:38.645
我很抱歉。
I'm sorry.


717
01:24:45.042 --> 01:24:46.696
Eden。
Eden.


718
01:26:41.158 --> 01:26:42.682
别担心，波。
Don't worry, Bo.


719
01:26:44.161 --> 01:26:46.555
在玉米地里什么都不会死。
Nothing ever really dies in the corn.